'You were right to bring this to me, [placeholder]! This belongs to no child, much less a Dunlending. This most certainly belongs to a hobbit!\n\n'The mystery, I'm afraid, has deepened.'
Talk to a Ranger at Echad Idhrenfair
There are Rangers at Echad Idhrenfair in the Gloomglens.\n\nYou should bring the object you found to the Rangers of the Grey Company. Perhaps they will be able to unravel the mystery.
